{"tid":2178613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"頻遭境外網路攻擊 紐西蘭證交所連4天暫停交易","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:01:42.000Z","uid":305299,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78e56efe4efae915e836e45ed373c58e3e228df2","tid":2178613,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4p5a77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4p5a77.jpg&h=6694243d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（法新社威靈頓28日電） 網路攻擊迫使紐西蘭證券交易所（NZX）今天連續第4天暫停交易，紐西蘭政府通訊安全局（GCSB）將協助防止網路安全受到侵害。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭證交所在聲明中表示：「我們目前面臨連線問題，跟本週<span class=\"red\">來自境外</span>嚴重的分散式阻斷服務（DDoS）攻擊類似。」<br />\n<br />\n分散式阻斷服務攻擊是藉由大量網路流量來癱瘓電腦網路系統。從25日起每天都發生類似攻擊，造成交易所暫時停止交易。<br />\n<br />\n儘管紐西蘭證交所在開市前，採取額外措施維持連線，今天仍無法如期交易。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭證交所說：「為了解決近期的網路攻擊問題，紐西蘭證交所持續與網路服務供應商Spark和政府通訊安全局等國家與國際網路安全夥伴合作。」<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭情報機關的政府通訊安全局任務，是防止境內的基礎建設受到網路攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n電腦網路系統中斷發生在財報季期間，這段時間通常是紐西蘭證交所最為繁忙的時候。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭證交所仍對這起攻擊的幕後主使者是誰三緘其口。<br />\n<br />\n專家曾告訴當地媒體有以下可能：由國家在背後撐腰的入侵事件、國際駭客組織「匿名」（Anonymous）等以反資本主義為訴求的網路攻擊，或勒索贖金的犯罪組織。（譯者：陳昱婷/核稿：徐睿承）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%80%A34%E5%A4%A9%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-060502650.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2589%2580%25E9%2580%25A34%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593-060502650.html&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=3b82db93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%80%A34%E5%A4%A9%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-060502650.html</a>"},{"pid":"34107a0a1a72adda47069889036319f2212907fa","tid":2178613,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"Channel手足被捕？我一早就話......架啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2178601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2178601</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"309f8d38f0e549104aacd49e5a6eebe4632d8e9f","tid":2178613,"uid":46933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇都知邊個國家做"},{"pid":"4b63d40702345deec4217abd908cf5c8cf9a160a","tid":2178613,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"邊有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332fec32776dadaec38ffd2a86989d463f1ca61","tid":2178613,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"「由國家在背後撐腰的入侵事件」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04b0637b8e254d98bc0e9235e1a8d6f3f6e1af5","tid":2178613,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"309f8d38f0e549104aacd49e5a6eebe4632d8e9f","tid":2178613,"uid":46933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇都知邊個國家做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e05940c878a6cd198419f799f761012ebafa3cc","tid":2178613,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"CCP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7a9b26737189905a777653aedfa81a1a23